ttp_template:
<group name="seq_action_network_netmask">
   seq {{SEQ}} {{ACTION}} {{NETWORK}}/{{NETMASK | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="seq_action_network_netmask_le">
   seq {{SEQ}} {{ACTION}} {{NETWORK}}/{{NETMASK}} le {{LE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="seq_action_network_netmask_ge_le">
   seq {{SEQ}} {{ACTION}} {{NETWORK}}/{{NETMASK}} ge {{GE}} le {{LE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
ip prefix-list OSPF_Redist: 2 entries
   seq 5 deny 10.0.0.0/24
   seq 10 permit 0.0.0.0/0 le 32
   seq 15 deny 10.0.0.0/8 ge 10 le 20
textfsm_template:
Value Required,Filldown NAME (\S+)
Value Required SEQ (\d+)
Value ACTION (\S+)
Value NETWORK ([0-9a-f:\.]+)
Value NETMASK (\d+)
Value LE (\d+)
Value GE (\d+)

Start
  ^ip\s+prefix-list\s+${NAME}:
  ^\s+seq\s+${SEQ}\s+${ACTION}\s+${NETWORK}/${NETMASK}(?:\s+ge\s+${GE}|)(?:\s+le\s+${LE}|)\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*$$
  # Capture time-stamp if vty line has command time-stamping turned on
  ^Load\s+for\s+
  ^Time\s+source\s+is
  ^.+ -> Error
